sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant UI as Login UI
    participant RT as Redux Thunk
    participant BE as Backend API
    participant NAV as Navigation

    U->>UI: Navigate to /login
    UI->>U: Render login form
    U->>UI: Enter "Username or Email" and "Password"
    U->>UI: Click "Login"
    UI->>RT: Dispatch login action
    RT->>BE: POST /api/login with credentials
    alt Successful Authentication
      BE-->>RT: Return user profile and set cookies
      RT->>UI: Update global state with user data
      UI->>NAV: Call navigate('/profile')
      Note over UI,NAV: User is logged in and session is maintained
    else Failed Authentication
      BE-->>RT: Return error message
      RT->>UI: Return error payload
      UI->>U: Display error message ("Invalid username or password")
    end
